{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_07_03",
  "title": "LizNoir 07 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoir握手会開催日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――LizNoir Handshake Event Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.6000001669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、今日も来てくれたのね。ありがとう\nこれからも応援よろしくね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you came again today. Thank you.\nPlease continue to support us",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.2666668336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "はーい、もっとこころを好きになれ～好きになれ～\nそして追加のアイドルスマイル～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-kay‚ love Kokoro more~ love more~\nAnd a bonus idol smile~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.3333335002
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "握手ですね、喜んで！\n今なら腕相撲のサービスもついてきますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A handshake‚ you say? Gladly!\nNow you can even get an arm-wrestling service!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.1333335002
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "…………握手？　あ、ごめん、ぼーっとしてた\nもちろんいいよ。はい。来てくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……A handshake? Oh‚ sorry‚ I was spacing out\nOf course it's fine. Yes. Thank you for coming",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.3000016928
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "（……葵）\n（握手会に参加してくれたのは嬉しいけど、上の空ね……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Aoi）\n（I'm glad she participated in the handshake event‚ but she's out of mind…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.6166706483
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.6166706483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "葵。さっきの態度は良くないわ\nせっかく来てくれたファンの方に失礼よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi. That attitude just now was not good\nIt's rude to the fans who went out of their way to come",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.2000039816
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は大事な仕事って聞いたから顔を出したんだ\nまだ僕も、LizNoirのメンバーだからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I came because I heard it was an important job today\nI'm still‚ a member of LizNoir",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.0000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.9333388408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "『まだ』って……冗談でもそんなこと言わないで\nファンとの交流はアイドルとしてとても大切な仕事よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Still\"… don't say things like that even as a joke\nInteracting with fans is a very important job for an idol",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.9333388408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "……それは分かってる。でも、大会は目前でしょ？\n他にやるべきことがあるんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I know it. But the tournament is right around the corner‚ isn't it?\nDon't we have other things we should be doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ファンサービスはもちろん大切だ\nでも僕らはアイドルであり、そしてパフォーマーだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fan service is certainly important\nBut we are idols and performers",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.400011611
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "早く調子を取り戻して、最高のパフォーマンスを見せる\n――それが、一番のファンサービスじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Recovering our condition quickly and showing our best performance\n――That's the best fan service there is‚ don't you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.8666734059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.3333424012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "大会に参加しない僕なんかが言うことじゃないけど……\n出るからには、三人には頑張ってほしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not my place to say this since I'm not participating in the tournament…\nsince you're going to participate‚ I want you three to do your best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1333375294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.8666803121
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう、葵。でもね、何度も言ってるけど\n今回はパフォーマンスだけで勝敗が決まる訳じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you‚ Aoi. But you know‚ as I've said many times‚\nthis time win and lose aren't decided by performance alone",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.6000087737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.0666803121
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ファンからの得票数が勝敗に大きく影響するの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The number of votes from fans greatly influences the outcome",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0666803121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.6666803121
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "私達だけじゃない。トリエルも他のアイドル達も\n積極的にプロモーションを行っているわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not just us. TRINITYAiLE and other idols‚ too\nThey are also actively promoting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3000058491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.1000136454
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、無様なパフォーマンスしか出来ない\n今の僕達が人気投票だけで勝ったとしても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But‚ even if we‚ who can only do a terrible performance now\nwin by popularity vote alone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6000058491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.4000136454
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなのは、僕達のLizNoirじゃない\nねぇ莉央。BIG4になるのって、そんなに大事？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "that wouldn't be our LizNoir\nHey Rio. Is becoming BIG4‚ really that important?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.0000058491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.4333540995
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "……えぇ、大事よ。私達アイドルにとって最高の栄誉で\n目指すべき頂。そんなの葵だって分かってるでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ it's important. It's the greatest honor for us idols\nand the peak we should set a goal. Aoi‚ you know that‚ don't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.3000129699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.7333540995
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "貴方やこころ、愛にとっても、今が一番大事な時期なの\n四人で全力を尽くして、BIG4になりましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For you‚ Kokoro‚ and Ai‚ now is the most important time\nLet's all give it our all as a team of four and become BIG4",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.5000129699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.2000044901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あの！　私にはどっちが正しいのかは分かりません\n……けど、葵さんと一緒にステージに立ちたいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Hey! I don't know which side is right\n…but I want to stand on the stage with Aoi-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.9000129699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.4000044901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
