      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 333.3666782774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、泣かないで。はい、ハンカチどうぞ\n貴方のせいではないんだし、気に病む必要はないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Hey‚ don't cry. Here‚ have this handkerchief\nIt's not your fault‚ so you don't have to worry about it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 338.86668574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 342.8666782774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-ranran007.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり……莉央さんは優しくて素敵な方ですね\nそんな人がリーダー失格だなんて私は思いません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As I thought… Rio-san‚ you're such a kind and wonderful person\nI don't think a person like that is a failure as a leader",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 349.6333524066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そう？　ありがとう……。自分に自信が持てなく\nなりかけていたところだったから……嬉しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Really? Thank you… I was starting to lose confidence\nin myself‚ so this makes me happy",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 359.06668574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 362.4999892311
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-ranran008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あの……莉央さん……！　実は私……\n……やっぱりなんでもないです……すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ um… Rio-san…! Actually‚ I…\n…It's nothing after all… I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 370.86668574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの？　途中でやめられたら気になるじゃない\n何か困ってることがあるなら私で良ければ聞くわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is that? I wonder if you'll stop midway\nIf you're having some trouble‚ I can listen if you want",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 379.1000190733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 383.3999749897
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-ranran009.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか……？　でも、莉央さんもお忙しいし\n事務所も違う私なんかが相談したら迷惑になるかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really…? But‚ Rio-san is busy‚ and\nit might be a bother if someone like me from a different agency consulted you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 388.76668574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 393.8999912658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "私がいいって言ってるんだからいいのよ\nほら、話してごらんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said it's fine‚ so it's fine\nCome on‚ tell me",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 397.3000190733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-ranran010.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、莉央さんに私の相談を\n聞いてもらえるなんて……夢みたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ to think that Rio-san would listen to my worries…\nit's like a dream",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 403.9666898089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-ranran011.m4a",
      "text": "実は私、今の事務所に悩みを相談出来る人が一人も\nいなくて。問題を起こした事務所ですし、不安で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ there's no one in my current agency that I can talk to about my worries\nOur agency caused a problem‚ so I'm feeling anxious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 413.2666898089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 419.0666070697
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだったの。大変だったわね\nそれで、何に悩んでいるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see. That must have been difficult\nSo‚ what are you worried about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 423.5666816709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 426.6666070697
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-ranran012.m4a",
      "text": "それが……あっ、いけない、そろそろ行かないと……！\nあの……良かったら連絡先を交換してもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That is… ah‚ I shouldn't‚ I have to go soon…!\nExcuse me… If it's okay with you‚ could we swap phone number?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 432.7000150042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-ranran013.m4a",
      "text": "メッセで相談出来たらな……って思ったんですけど\n敵同士ですし……難しい……ですよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it would be nice if I could consult you through messages…\nWe're rivals… so I guess it would be difficult…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 442.4666816709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 447.1666436909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "問題ないわよ。……でも、馴れ合うつもりはないわ\n大会で当たっても、手は抜かないからそのつもりでね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's no problem. …But‚ I'm not going to be friendly\nEven if we face each other in the tournament‚ I won't go easy on you‚ so beware",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 452.5000150042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-ranran014.m4a",
      "text": "はい、莉央さん達と当たるのを楽しみにしています\n勝てる気はまるでしませんけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'm looking forward to facing you and your group\nI don't feel like I can win at all‚ though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 461.1000150042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 464.2666335183
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "もう、今からそんな弱気でどうするの？\n勝つ気持ちは、途切れさせたら絶対ダメよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my‚ why are you so timid already?\nYou can never let go of the feeling of wanting to win",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 468.6000150042,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3599.9809267000273,
          "startTime": 472.1999959309
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 472.0333483376
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、良かった。莉央さんまだいてくれた。やっぱり\nもう一度、葵さんと話してもらった方が……ってあれ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ that's good. Rio-san is still here. I was thinking that maybe\nyou should talk to Aoi-san one more time… huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 476.7666816709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 481.6999342995
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "うーーん……？　あの人、確か以前、こころ達に\n嫌がらせしたプロダクションのアイドル……だよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm…? That person‚ I think they're an idol from the production\nthat harassed us before… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 486.6666816709,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}